title: Ep. 2854 - Bhide Is Going Through A Bad Time - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 4 November 2019
shortDesc: Bhide loses his home keys and Madhvi is searching for it. Several people come to give bills. After a while, Bhide goes on to start Sakharam but it doesn't start. In the end, Sodhi shows him that he didn't even put in the keys. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2855 - Theft At Bhide's House - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 5 November 2019
shortDesc: Bhide comes back home and finds out that his house is in a mess and the jewelry is missing. Even Madhvi is missing from the house. Bhide is tensed and all the people gather to help. Chalu Pandey is called to the scene. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2856 - The Intense Investigation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 6 November 2019
shortDesc: Chalu Pandey is trying to solve the case. Bhide tries to explain and Chalu Pandey listens carefully. Jethalal comes and creates confusion but soon the confusion is cleared and the investigation continues. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2857 - The Questioning Session - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 7 November 2019
shortDesc: Chalu Pandey takes a step back and starts asking questions to each and everyone involved. He calls upon the people who had visited the society. When Chalu Pandey is leaving the blue car that is the primary suspect drives into the society.

title: Ep. 2858 - Madhvi Clarifies The Doubt - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 8 November 2019
shortDesc: The blue car comes in and Madhvi comes out of it and explains that she had gone out with her friend. She also tells the people that it was she who kept the jewellery in the bank locker. The confusion is cleared. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2859 - Jethalal Gets Scolded - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 11 November 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal wakes up late and gets trouble with his hair and asks Tappu to help him out with that. Tappu gives him some hair gel and Jethalal gets out for his meeting with a client.

title: Ep. 2860 - Sodhi's Announcement - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 12 November 2019
shortDesc: Sodhi comes with the Dholak and is very happy. He calls everyone downstairs to announce something special. He tells everyone that he has organized for a Kirtana Session in respect to Guru Nanak Jayanti the next to next day.

title: Ep. 2861 - Nattu Kaka Wants A Holiday - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 13 November 2019
shortDesc: Nattu Kaka and Baga are invited by Sodhi to the program. Baga and Nattu Kaka ask Jethalal for a holiday the next day. Jethalal denies them the holiday. Sodhi forgets a major part of the preparation. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2862 - The Keertana Programme - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 14 November 2019
shortDesc: The langar has been prepared and everyone gets ready for the program. The program is amazing and everyone is spiritually replenished. The next morning Jethalal has a problem with his phone bill. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2863 - Jethalal's New Shirt - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 15 November 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal meets Iyer and Babita in the morning and Babita compliments his shirt. Later Abdul also praises the look of the shirt. However, Bhide rides Sakharam over a puddle and the mud is spilt on his shirt. Jethalal gets a threatening call.

title: Ep. 2864 - Calls Diversion To Jethalal's Phone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 18 November 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal continues to get calls from people asking him money. Sundar comes to his shop and informs him that his friend had diverted all calls from Sundar's number to Jethalal's phone. This was because Sundar's phone was broken. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2865 - A Bad Day For Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 19 November 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal has a bad day at work already and then comes home. He is also upset that Babita couldn't come to his shop. Later he searches for pickle in the kitchen and misses Daya. Tapu also tells about a night out for completing a group project.

title: Ep. 2866 - Baga's Dream - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 20 November 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal is in a bad mood after the entire day and he also gets scolding from Champaklal. Jethalal is mocked by Iyer and as a result, they have a heavy quarrel. Later Baga sees a dream on a full moon night. He tells Jethalal about it.

title: Ep. 2867 - Jethalal Breaks Champaklal's Specs - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 21 November 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal comes to check on his father at night when he breaks the specs. Champaklal has no spare specs and hence Jethalal has to guide him everywhere for the next day. Jethalal sleeps with his father so that he can wake up early and help his father.

title: Ep. 2868 - Babita And Jethalal's Exercise Session - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 22 November 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal takes Champaklal for his morning walk and sees that Babita is also doing her morning exercises. He goes and joins her and finds out that Iyer is also present. Jethalal has a great exercise session in the morning with them.
